### 1. 登录接口（获取 Token）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/atm/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNo": "6222020000000001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. 账户信息查询接口（新接口）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/atm/account/info?token=REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID

### 2.1 账户信息查询接口（兼容旧前端）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/atm/accounts/profile?sessionId=REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID

### 3. 余额查询接口（新接口）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/atm/account/balance?token=REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID

### 3.1 余额查询接口（兼容旧前端）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/atm/accounts/balance?sessionId=REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID

### 4. 退出登录接口（兼容 token / sessionId）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/atm/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID"
}
